# Functions

## Modules

A module is a set of functions.

```elixir
defmodule Mathematics do

  def sum(x, y) do # arity is 2
    x + y
  end

  def multiply(x, y) do # arity is 2
    x * y
  end

  def multiply(x, y, z) do # arity is 3
    x * y * z
  end
  
end
```

## (Named) Functions

```elixir
Mathematics.sum(3,4)
```

```elixir
Mathematics.multiply(7,8)
```

```elixir
Mathematics.multiply(10, 3, 2)
```

