## Anonymous Functions

```elixir
fn(x) -> x*2 end
```

```elixir
f = fn(x) -> x*3 end
```

```elixir
f.(3)
```

```elixir
g = fn(x,y,z) -> (x+y)*z end
```

```elixir
g.(2,3,10)
```

```elixir
x = 10
h = fn(y) -> x+y end
x = 20
h.(20)
